OL,6,FBut he says both he and the 19,000-
OL,7,Fstrong team at Betsi "share the same
OL,8,Fambition to make lasting improvements
OL,9,Fin the health and the wellbeing of the
OL,10,Fpopulation of North Wales and the
OL,11,Fprovision of their healthcare
OL,12,Fservices."
OL,14,FHealth Minister Eluned Morgan made the
OL,15,Fannouncement saying Mr Edwards would
OL,16,F"continue to bring a wealth of
OL,17,Fexperience and knowledge to the board
OL,18,Fand will continue to build upon the
OL,19,Fexcellent foundations he has put in
OL,20,Fplace over the last 11 months."
