OL,6,FThe entire board were removed from
OL,7,Ftheir positions. That was met with
OL,8,Fcriticism, with the Welsh
OL,9,FConservatives calling for a "total
OL,10,Fclear out of this dysfunctional
OL,11,Fexecutive team."
OL,13,FHealth boards in Wales are made up of
OL,14,Fa team of independent members which
OL,15,Fholds an executive team to account.
OL,17,FRecruitment is now underway for a
OL,18,Ffurther four independent members,
OL,19,Fthese appointments will be announced
OL,20,Fin February.
