OL,6,FHealth Minister Eluned Morgan added:
OL,7,F"The full complement of board members
OL,8,Fwill ensure the board has the
OL,9,Fappropriate skills and expertise to
OL,10,Flead the organisation through Special
OL,11,FMeasures."
OL,13,FPlacing a health board into Special
OL,14,FMeasures does not mean the Welsh
OL,15,FGovernment takes over the day-to-day
OL,16,Frunning of the health board. That
OL,17,Fremains the responsibility of the
OL,18,Fboard.
