OL,6,Frefer to a range of actions which can
OL,7,Fbe taken to improve health boards or
OL,8,Ftrusts and specific NHS services in
OL,9,Fexceptional circumstances.
OL,11,FIt is the highest level of escalation
OL,12,Fand happens when a health board or
OL,13,Ftrust is not making the improvements
OL,14,Fexpected and there are concerns that
OL,15,Fthe leadership and management require
OL,16,Fexternal support to respond to the
OL,17,Fserious concerns identified.
