OL,6,FWelsh Conservative Shadow Minister for
OL,7,FNorth Wales, Darren Millar is hoping
OL,8,Fthe permanent appointment will bring
OL,9,Fmore stability to the health board.JHe
OL,10,Fsaid: "The Betsi Cadwaladr University
OL,11,FHealth Board is nearing yet another
OL,12,Fanniversary in special measures, but
OL,13,Fpatients and staff are yet to see the
OL,14,Fimprovements they have been promised
OL,15,Fby Labour Ministers.
